; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">A digital business card is the easiest way to share your contact details at conferences and expos like these. You can&nbsp;<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sgKVOBDDbBc\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">share your digital business card</a>&nbsp;via scanning the QR code on your business card, by text, email, pasting your link into your preferred messenger app, using a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rx8wKJACv6E\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">smartphone widget</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Hw1PJgeyi54\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Apple Watch integration</a>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The process is slick and your new contact can save your details directly to their phone. You and your team can even&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/how-to-create-and-use-a-dynamic-qr-code\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">download your cards QR code</a>&nbsp;to use wherever you like; name badges, trade stands, brochures, your website and socials even on traditional business cards.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Find out how a Blinq digital business card can help you interact with other content creators, streamers, influencers and more by creating your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">free digital business card today</a>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Create digital business cards for your team</h3><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you run a business or a team, you can use Blinq to create and manage digital business cards for your team. Using a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/business\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Blinq Business subscription</a>&nbsp;you’ll be able to design digital business cards for your team from a single dashboard. You’ll also be able to export all the contacts that your cards create to your existing CRM system and integrate Blinq with your Active Directory too.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Simple to set up and seamless to use, you and your team can try Blinq Business free for 30 days,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/pricing\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">click here</a>&nbsp;to get started.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Have you heard about NFC business cards?</h2><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you’re looking for a physical as well as a digital business card, Blinq has you covered. You can order a physical NFC business card at any time via your Blinq app or from our website.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">You can add your unique branding and visuals to design beautiful cards and simply tap them on a recipient\'s smartphone to share your contact details.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/nfc-business-card\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Click here to find out more</a>.</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><a id=\"create-digital-business-cards-for-your-team\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\"></a></p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Whichever conferences you and your team attend, have fun and take Blinq with you to help grow your network!</p>', '2022-12-11 11:22:07', '2022-12-11 13:35:02', 1, 1, 1, 6, 6, 'Read this post if you’d like to know how to create your very own NFC business card. Includes pricing and frequently asked questions.');
