bia/\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">BizCan Colombia</a></h2><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Where</span>: Medellin</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">When</span>: 21May - 22May</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">What</span>: Bridging the legislative gap between North and South America is a key theme at this event which brings together key voices from both sides of the continent.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Great for</span>: understanding where your specialism is best placed to take advantage of the legislative shift happening right now. Use your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">digital business card</a>&nbsp;to expand your network.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://bizcannexpo.com/tickets/\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Registration &amp; Pricing</a></p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">How can a digital business card help you network?</h2><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/solutions/digital-business-card\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">digital business card</a>&nbsp;is the easiest way to share your contact details. You can share your digital business card via scanning your QR code, by text, email, pasting your link into your preferred messenger app, using a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/solutions/widgets\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">smartphone widget</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/solutions/apple-watch\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Apple Watch integration</a>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The process is slick and your new contact can save your details directly to their phone. You and your team can even&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/blog/how-to-create-and-use-a-dynamic-qr-code\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">download your cards QR code</a>&nbsp;to use wherever you like; name badges, trade stands, brochures, your website and socials even on traditional business cards.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Create digital business cards for your team</h3><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you run a business or a team, you can use Blinq to create and manage digital business cards for your team. Using a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/business\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Blinq Business subscription</a>&nbsp;you’ll be able to design digital business cards for your team from a single dashboard. You’ll also be able to export all the contacts that your cards create to your existing CRM system and integrate Blinq with your Active Directory too.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Simple to set up and seamless to use, you can try Blinq Business free for 30 days,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/pricing\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">click here</a>&nbsp;to get started.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Can I add my digital business card contacts to my CRM system?</h3><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">With Blinq, you can add the contacts you make to your CRM system, quickly and easily.</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Blinq Premium users can download a CSV file of the contacts that they make and upload this to their CRM system.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://blinq.me/business\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Blinq Business</a>&nbsp;users can add their contacts to their existing CRM system at any time using Zapier. The setup takes around 5 minutes and allows you to connect Blinq with thousands of CRM systems including, HubSpot, Salesforce, Monday.com, Zoho, Microsoft Dynamics and many more.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">To export your contacts using Blinq:</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><ul role=\"list\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 40px; overflow: hidden; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li>Open your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dash.blinq.me/\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Blinq dashboard</a>&nbsp;and login (note: only Blinq Business Admins can export contacts for their organization to their CRM).&nbsp;</li><li>Go to the “Contacts” view</li><li>Click “Export Contacts”&nbsp;</li><li>Choose either as CSV or Zapier</li><li>Download the file or follow the simple steps to setup the integration</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you would like to Demo Blinq Business with us, please get in contact today&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/contact\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">using this link</a>.</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">Have you heard about NFC business cards?</h2><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you’re looking for a physical as well as a digital business card, Blinq has you covered. You can order a physical NFC business card at any time via your Blinq app or from our website.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">You can add your unique branding to design beautiful cards and simply tap them on a recipient\'s smartphone to share your contact details.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/nfc-business-card\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">Click here to find out more</a>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><a id=\"create-digital-business-cards-for-your-team\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\"></a><a id=\"can-i-add-my-digital-business-card-contacts-to-my-crm-system-\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\"></a></p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p>', '2022-12-11 11:23:40', '2022-12-11 13:34:20', 1, 1, 1, 6, 5, 'Read this post if you’d like to know how to create your very own NFC business card. Includes pricing and frequently asked questions.');
