 rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">4. how to add key information fields.&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">‍</h2><figure class=\"w-richtext-figure-type-video w-richtext-align-center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 60%; width: 551.688px; height: 0px; clear: both; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; padding-bottom: 310.078px;\"><div style=\"font-size: 0px; color: transparent; width: 551.688px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8zhwXeQWpoo\" title=\"How to set up your free Blinq digital business card\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 551.688px; height: 310.078px;\"></iframe></div></figure><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">What do I put on my digital business card?</h2><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">1. Name and Profile Picture</h3><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Our digital business cards allow you to customize the way you want to be addressed. Outside of your first name and last name. We help you list the information that matters to you - so you can share the way you would like to show up in the world. Such as your preferred pronouns, preferred names and much more.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p