-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(39, 40, 41); font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\">10. Attribution and Interaction Tracking</h3><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://blinq.me/business\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">For businesses</a>, return on investment is of paramount importance. Our CRM Integrations also allow you to automatically track the meetings your team has had and the new contacts that they create. Track star performers within your teams and reward them for their efforts.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">You can also receive live updates when prospects change their contact details if they have the Blinq app. Digital business cards now give businesses measurable data on how and where their network is growing, letting you see where your networking efforts (and spend) are best utilized.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">If you want top rated digital business card software and a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blinq.me/nfc-business-card\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">physical NFC business card</a>&nbsp;too, Blinq is the best choice for you and your business.</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br></p><figure class=\"w-richtext-figure-type-video w-richtext-align-center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 60%; width: 551.688px; height: 0px; clear: both; color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; padding-bottom: 413.766px;\"><div style=\"font-size: 0px; color: transparent; width: 551.688px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QzdFUhl0XfM\" title=\"Create your Blinq NFC business card\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 551.688px; height: 413.766px;\"></iframe></div></figure><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">‍</p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Networking has changed. Make sure you and your team have a&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://blinq.me/solutions/digital-business-card\" style=\"color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;\">digital business card</a><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;ready to share as part of your networking toolkit.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgba(39, 40, 41, 0.75); font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><a id=\"1-name-and-profile-picture\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\"></a><a id=\"2-contact-details-email-phone\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\"></a><a id=\"3-company-details-job-title-logo-and-company-name\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(243, 90, 87); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-family: Avenirnext, sans-serif;\"></a><a id=\"4-website-marketing-materials\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: